# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  WebGap / BizFinder — API Keys
#  Copy this file to ".env" (in the same folder as WebGap.exe)
#  and fill in your keys.  install.bat will do this for you
#  automatically the first time you run it.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# REQUIRED for AI-powered observations + smart follow-up replies.
# Get yours at: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# REQUIRED for the business search itself — Google Places API.
# Get yours at: https://console.cloud.google.com
# Enable: "Places API", "Places API (New)", "Geocoding API", "Maps JavaScript API"
GOOGLE_API_KEY=

# OPTIONAL — Yelp review fallback (fires when Google finds no reviews).
# Free tier: 500 requests/day.  Get yours at:
# https://www.yelp.com/developers
YELP_API_KEY=

# OPTIONAL — Stripe payment link generator.
# Creates a one-click Stripe checkout link for each prospect.
# Use your SECRET key (starts with sk_live_ or sk_test_).
# Get yours at: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
